div.p: In input string >==, the scanner reaches index 0.

ul.li: Maximal Munch: Prefers source[0:2] (>=) as a single valid operator.
Non-Greedy: Prefers source[0:1] (>), leaving == as a separate token.

div.p: Maximal Munch is mandatory to prevent the parser from receiving ambiguous operators as separate assignment/comparison tokens.
FAILED TO PEEK. Logic exits greediness loop early.
